subtitle: beloved Masters most of you are now
aware that in the beginning stages of
the initiation process there is somewhat
of a crisis as the battle for Supremacy
begins between the ego desire
personality and the Soul self
each person must Endeavor to clear his
or her illusionary distorted reality of
the astral planes of consciousness
the ego desired personality is
controlled by the energies and impulses
of the three lower chakras and these out
of balance inclinations must be brought
under control of the Soul self once more
this period is often called The Dark
Knight of the Soul or traversing The
Valley Of Shadows when you are in the
midst of the process it is important
that you understand you are not being
punished dear one after you have
successfully traversed the shadow lands
and emerged triumphant you will look
back in retrospect and you will realize
that you were given a great opportunity
a wonderful gift of growth
a spiritual aspirant is a consciously
aware human being who is seeking
Enlightenment and self-mastery and in
the beginning stages he or she is
somewhat
self-focused often prone to temper and
irritability and frustration and may
experience bouts of self-doubt and
depression
a spiritual aspirant must develop
sensitivity and a loving understanding
nature the aspirant's purpose will
gradually move away from the personal
ambition and love of power into a desire
to be of service to humanity a desire to
serve others is a soul Instinct Brave
bearers of light are you ready and
willing to be a Pathfinder to open the
doors to the many Heavenly mansions and
many dimensions of creation each High
dimensional level offers newer
opportunities and will give you access
to many new abilities and expanded
wisdom however each higher level will
also challenge you in many ways and will
require that you release those things
which no longer serve your greatest good
you left many facets of your greatest
self along the way as you Traverse the
descending pathway into the lower
dimensions and you now must be willing
to release to the past those people ways
of being and things which do not fit
into your present and future reality as
you make your return journey into the
higher dimensions
my faithful ones we are assisting you in
every way possible within the limits of
the universal laws and we are waiting
patiently for you to join us in the
various pyramids of light station
throughout this sub-universe
we have told you that you are not only
creating your new Earthly reality but
you are also preparing yourselves to
take up full residency in a world that
is glorious Beyond Your Wildest
imagining
we convey to you all the radiance of
Creator light and love you can contain
now you are loved deeply loved Beyond a
measure
I am Archangel Michael
so be it
